# SROIE 2019 Dataset Description

This repository uses the **ICDAR 2019 SROIE (Scanned Receipts OCR and Information Extraction)** dataset. The dataset is a benchmark commonly used for document image understanding, layout analysis, optical character recognition (OCR), and structured information extraction from unstructured document text.

## Dataset Overview
* **Domain:** Document Intelligence / Document Text Processing
* **Task:** Text Detection, Optical Character Recognition (OCR), and Information Extraction (IE) from scanned receipts.
* **Format:** Raw receipt images matching with token-level bounding boxes (`.txt`) and clean entity labels (`.txt`).
* **Language:** English

---

## Data Structure & Contents

The original dataset is typically split into training and evaluation sets. For every individual receipt sample, three parallel files are available:

1. **Scanned Images (`.jpg`):** High-resolution scans of physical retail receipts featuring diverse fonts, text alignments, layout deformations, and OCR noise conditions.
